info:

        "200":
          description: "Ok"
components:

    apiKeyHeader:
      type: apiKey
      name: Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key
      in: header
    apiKeyQuery:
      type: apiKey
      name: subscription-key
      in: query
security:
  - apiKeyHeader: []
  - apiKeyQuery: []
